comment.body: Vremya i steklo (time and glass) is a pun on vremya isteklo (время истекло, time's up).

You can find several masters at rutracker. Here's 404 song: https://rutracker.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=5150048
I used it for H.265 encoding tests. You can compress it to ~40 MB H.265 video without significant quality loss!
